cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SD 

This paper deals with natural language processing and reinforcement learning in the context of a complex strategy game, StarCraft II. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of deep neural networks and embeddings could also place it under cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.SD (Software Engineering).
